polished glass,

971
01:08:57,642 --> 01:09:01,642
笑って輝いていたいだけで
I just want to smile and shine.

972
01:09:09,142 --> 01:09:11,142
「誰のためだっけ」
"For whose sake was it?"

973
01:09:15,042 --> 01:09:17,842
声が 姿が
My voice, my form...

974
01:09:17,842 --> 01:09:20,642
誰でもない気がした
I felt like I was no one.

975
01:09:21,242 --> 01:09:23,142
「孤独だ」って
"I'm alone,"

976
01:09:23,342 --> 01:09:25,242
また迷い出す
I start to get lost again.

977
01:09:25,242 --> 01:09:28,042
画面の奥の瞳を
At the eyes deep in the screen,

978
01:09:28,042 --> 01:09:29,242
いつでも
always,

979
01:09:29,442 --> 01:09:31,642
いつでも 君は
always, you...

980
01:09:32,542 --> 01:09:35,442
映す光の中に
Inside the light that reflects,

981
01:09:35,842 --> 01:09:40,042
名もない私の声を見つけてくれてた
you were finding my nameless voice.

982
01:09:41,842 --> 01:09:43,142
ずっと
Always.

983
01:09:54,342 --> 01:09:57,442
この声も 姿も
This voice, and this form too,

984
01:09:57,442 --> 01:10:01,242
紛れもない私だ
is unmistakably me.

985
01:10:00,178 --> 01:10:01,478
この声も、姿も、
This voice, and this form,

986
01:10:01,478 --> 01:10:03,278
ありのままでいいんだ
It's okay to be just as I am.

987
01:10:03,278 --> 01:10:07,678
この気持ちは本物だ
This feeling is real.

988
01:10:07,678 --> 01:10:11,378
縛られても
Even if I'm tied down,

989
01:10:11,378 --> 01:10:18,678
触れられなくても
Even if I can't be touched.

990
01:10:19,278 --> 01:10:26,678
君が示してくれてたから
Because you showed me the way.

991
01:10:28,678 --> 01:10:33,978
いつかこの「私」で
Someday, as this "me",

992
01:10:34,678 --> 01:10:40,978
ずっと光を手繰って
I'll keep pulling in the light.

993
01:10:40,978 --> 01:10:44,378
きっと見つけ出す
I'll surely find it,

994
01:10:44,378 --> 01:10:48,178
誰でもない「君」に会えるまで
Until I can meet the "you" who is no one else.

995
01:10:48,178 --> 01:10:54,678
境界線はすぐそこに
The boundary line is right there.

996
01:10:59,378 --> 01:11:00,478
そう
Yes,

997
01:11:00,478 --> 01:11:02,278
画面の向こう
beyond the screen.

998
01:11:02,278 --> 01:11:02,978
繋ぎたい
I want to connect,

999
01:11:02,978 --> 01:11:03,678
越えたい
I want to cross over,

1000
01:11:03,678 --> 01:11:05,278
触れたい
I want to touch,

1001
01:11:05,278 --> 01:11:06,678
それこそ
that is...

1002
01:11:06,678 --> 01:11:09,278
それこそ私なんだ
That is exactly who I am.

1003
01:11:09,278 --> 01:11:12,278
「君」と光になって
Becoming light with "you",

1004
01:11:12,278 --> 01:11:15,678
未だ遮る硝子の壁の先まで
To beyond the glass wall that still blocks us.

1005
01:11:17,178 --> 01:11:21,678
届くように笑っていたい
I want to keep smiling so it reaches you.

1006
01:11:22,678 --> 01:11:26,278
迷いはない
There is no hesitation.

1007
01:11:26,278 --> 01:11:31,678
君がくれたこの感情と
With this emotion you gave me.

1008
01:11:31,678 --> 01:11:36,678
あー
Ah-

